  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667030/extras/606b79ab4124807cd06a05e2c88edcc8.avif?t=1537441344\" width=614 height=336 /></span></h2>The great researcher Archimedes had been living in Syracuse  when one of his experiments destroyed the entire city. <br>He was tasked to recover the land. Ancient Greece. The city of Syracuse.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667030/extras/bb7782393c18f589f2ec40101e919932.avif?t=1537441344\" width=614 height=180 /></span></h2>The great researcher Archimedes starts a field test of his new invention, which is a winch powered by wind. Hercules competes with the mechanism, and loses!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667030/extras/cd3977c956b264ff94a0a87a7bc220d1.avif?t=1537441344\" width=614 height=180 /></span></h2>All of a sudden, a gush of wind breaks the device which, in turn, destroying the whole city.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667030/extras/119a419613b9991a9cfadff2c51217ea.avif?t=1537441344\" width=614 height=180 /></span></h2>It’s now Archimedes task to recover the land. He succeeds, but who says he has no more inventions?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667030/extras/2e4db3d46f3ba768891431a068c13ea4.avif?t=1537441344\" width=614 height=174 /></span></h2>Features:<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Build estate & get revenue<br></li><li> The game is easy to learn, yet challenging to master<br></li><li> An alternative point of view to great researcher Archimedes<br></li><li> 100 different levels to discover<br></li><li> Devices, bridges, portals, zip lines<br></li><li> Marvellous comics</li></ul><br>Want to translate Archimedes into your own language? Let us know!",
